columns.name: event_date
columns.desc: The date on which the event was logged

columns.name: event_timestamp
columns.desc: The time (in microseconds, UTC) at which the event was logged on the client

columns.name: event_name
columns.desc: The name of the event

columns.name: event_params
columns.desc: A repeated record of the parameters associated with this event

columns.name: event_previous_timestamp
columns.desc: The time (in microseconds, UTC) at which the event was previously logged on the client

columns.name: event_value_in_usd
columns.desc: The currency-converted value (in USD) of the event's value parameter

columns.name: event_bundle_sequence_id
columns.desc: The sequential ID of the bundle in which these events were uploaded

columns.name: event_server_timestamp_offset
columns.desc: Timestamp offset between collection time and upload time in micros

columns.name: user_id
columns.desc: The user ID set via the setUserId API

columns.name: user_pseudo_id
columns.desc: The pseudonymous id (e.g., app instance ID) for the user

columns.name: user_properties
columns.desc: A repeated record of user properties set with the setUserProperty API

columns.name: user_first_touch_timestamp
columns.desc: The time (in microseconds) at which the user first opened the app or visited the site

columns.name: user_ltv
columns.desc: A record of Lifetime Value information about the user

columns.name: device
columns.desc: A record of device information

columns.name: geo
columns.desc: A record of the user's geographic information

columns.name: app_info
columns.desc: A record of information on the app

columns.name: traffic_source
columns.desc: Name of the traffic source that first acquired the user

columns.name: stream_id
columns.desc: The numeric ID of the stream

columns.name: platform
columns.desc: The platform on which the app was built

columns.name: event_dimensions
columns.desc: Dimensions associated with the event

columns.name: ecommerce
columns.desc: A record of information about ecommerce

columns.name: items
columns.desc: A repeated record of items included in this event
